name: RRRRRREPLAY
description:
Manually made switches on mirror filter over a pre-glitched video. The entire flow is made by fingers on screen during the complete 1:53min, rhythm and tone attempted to be set by heart. 

+ Exploration of the interesting feeling of how an aesthetic experience seems to present itself when an almost or entirely 'automated' rhythm is achieved 'naturally' or 'manually'... and viceversa? +





RRRRRREPLAY
